~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : whois                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : whois [<site>/-r]

   This command allows the admin to check on a site to see if it is a 
   legitimate site that is listed with internic.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : finger, nslookup, accreq
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
